metadata.name: Naa Jaane  Kyun
metadata.description:
NAA JAANE KYU (1/1 Music Video NFT) 

Artist - Jerry ft Rishi Roy & Mufasa Rex
Prod - Snasa Music 
VIDEO - DINIMACK 
Executive producers - HH12 and HW 

At first , The song impersonates their lost love who seems to be engaged on some other call reflecting the feeling of love and loneliness. Then the Song conveys about a guy missing their other half and wanting them back. Further The video shows a boy listening to a song in the car and while sitting on bench wearing headphones the time seems to move slow in the rain which seems to reflect him being in his own head , not living in present but in the memories of a certain person.
Thank you!

Utilities-
1. Early Access to all upcoming projects from HH12 and Graffiti.
2. Free Exclusive Access to the YBM 2023 Show.
3. Special Mention in YouTube Discription of each song you collect.

This NFT Do Not Transfer any Intellectual Copyright Ownership To The Collector/Holder.
Song is available on YouTube and All Streaming Platform.
